        public TtFlags(java.lang.String phGroup,
               java.lang.String auxGroup,
               boolean isRegional,
               boolean isDepth,
               boolean canUse,
               boolean dis,
               TtStat ttStat,
               Ellip ellip,
               Ellip upEllip)
        Each phase is created all at once.
        Parameters:
        phGroup - Phase group
        auxGroup - Auxiliary (complementary) phase group
        isRegional - True if the phase is flagged as regional
        isDepth - True if the phase is depth sensitive
        canUse - True if the phase may be used in an earthquake location
        dis - True if the phase should be down weighted
        ttStat - Travel-time statistics object
        ellip - Ellipticity correction object
        upEllip - Ellipticity correction object for an associated up going branch if any
